{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Ever wanted to try yourself as a contestant in a cooking show? Then your time has come!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Your Culinary Talent</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249770/extras/cards_1.gif?t=1731497908\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Like all other rogue-like deck-building games, every attempt to become the Greatest Chef will involve a careful selection of skill cards, a choice of activities, collecting special items, and of course, cooking tactics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is not your home kitchen. Every dish you are about to cook can deal irreparable damage to your self-confidence, knocking you out of the competition.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Plan, decide and cook wisely to reach the final challenge fully prepared.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Tasty and Bold</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249770/extras/art_1.gif?t=1731497908\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">All visual content is handcrafted with great love for the world of culinary arts.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Elimination Rounds</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249770/extras/show_1.gif?t=1731497908\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will face a cooking competition round at the end of each game week. A unique challenge awaits you in each elimination round. Prepare a dish that will impress the jury, and your victory will give you a bonus for the next week. Otherwise, you will be removed from the competition.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249770/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731497908","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets